quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"∆Āattiimo yim…ďe …ďe hasboore ma…ď…ďe nde, te kam…ďe he…ďe e ndeer welsindaare ko …ďe …óuurnii…ďe."
  21,2,"Arataa e ma…ď…ďe waajo immorde ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe ko fu…ó…óaa si wonaa …ďe jentike nde kam…ďe he…ďe pija."
  21,3,"∆Āer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óe ko belsandii…óe …ďe too√Ī…ďe suu…óa cowndi(gunndo) [wi'a] enee, h oo wonu si wanaa …ďanndiŇčke yeru mo'on, kaa on ngarat ee mbilewu hara onon ho…óon nji'a (ndaara)?!"
  21,4,"O maaki: "Joomi am no anndi Konngol ngol ka kammu e ka Leydi KaŇčko ko o Nanoowo ganndu…óo on."
  21,5,"Ko woni, …ďe mbi'i i'u: "Ko nde jii…ďu-jaa…ďu koy…ói, toode, o fekindi nde, ko woni, kaŇčko ko o jimoowo, awa yo o addan en aayewal wano aran…ďe …ďen Nuliranoo non"."
  21,6,"GooŇč…óinaani ado ma…ď…ďe immorde e saare Min kalki nde. Enee, hara ko kam…ďe gooŇč…óita?"
  21,7,"Min Nulaani ado maa…óa si wonaa wor…ďe Min Wahayina e ma…ď…ďe, lanndee yim…ďe defte …ďe si tawii wonii on anndaa."
  21,8,"Min mba…óaani …ďe …ďalli …ďe √Īaamataa √Īaametee, …ďe laataaki kadi luttintee…ďe."
  21,9,"Refti Min nGoonginani …ďe Fodoore nde Min danndi …ďe won'dude e …ďen …ďe Min Muuyi, Min kalki fantin…ďe …ďen."
  21,10,"GooŇč…óii Min njippinii fa'ade e moo…óon deftere no e ndeer mayre jaŇčtawol moo…óon. Kaa on kakkiltaa."